ke alt kan m\u00e5les, sier Tots\u00e5s. Hun er skeptisk til om leseunders\u00f8kelsen som er gjennomf\u00f8rt gir et riktig bilde av hvor flinke elevene er til \u00e5 lese."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "forbruker"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "a0b5358bb1114af2fc1e0d2e5c3da90a99f4644807d7ade9f04082a4da9a197a"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2017-07-13T20:00:37.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Bare 20 timer er viet elevenes f\u00f8rste lese- og skriveoppl\u00e6ring. Likevel f\u00f8ler l\u00e6rerstudentene seg godt rustet. De vil leke fram barnas eget spr\u00e5k."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article1014904.ece5/ALTERNATES/w980-default/ver2%20Heimen%20og%20Tots%C3%A5s"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/442bd74d5e80a361c4681492fc919f306f0e8d78.jpg?5967d165"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": "Leker videre p\u00e5 l\u00e6rerutdanningen -adressa.no"}, {"field": "id", "value": "442bd74d5e80a361c4681492fc919f306f0e8d78"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["nyheter", "trondheim", "ukeadressa", "eadressa", "skattelister", "d\u00f8dsfall", "tr\u00f8nder", "trafikk"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "nyheter,trondheim,ukeadressa,eadressa,skattelister,d\u00f8dsfall,tr\u00f8nder,trafikk"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": "forbruker"}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "education"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["l\u00e6rt", "lese", "skriveoppl\u00e6ring", "lek", "barna", "leker videre"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["trondheims", "l\u00e6rerplan 97"]}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": ["laila heimen", "inger tots\u00e5s"]}, {"field": "kw-taxonomy", "value": "forbruker"}, {"field": "og-image", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article1014904.ece5/ALTERNATES/w9